ygData.subject: Re: Any price recommendations?
ygData.msgSnippet: I usually charge 1gp per level for bind and 5gp for enchanting silver. Everything else I do pretty much for free. ... From: vmjh Sent: Friday, April 30, 1999
ygData.messageBody:
I usually charge 1gp per level for bind and 5gp for enchanting silver.
Everything else I do pretty much for free.

-----Original Message-----
From: vmjh
Sent: Friday, April 30, 1999 1:38 PM
To: .EQ.Magic
Cc: vmjh
Subject: [_EQ_Magic] Any price recommendations?

From: Matthew Musingo <vmjh@...>

Many unelightened warriors have walked up to me and asked to be
binded/SOWed/get some food and water/invisible. Now, my question
is...what
is your recommendation as setting the price on these spells?

Oh, and on Fennin Ro, I love the guy in Qeynos who kept saying he was
insane and PAYING people to bind them. Forgot his name.

Kapolokok

the magic glade down in Dingly Dell. Here he sold contraceptives..."
-- Python
